    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>We report the identification of three structurally diverse compounds \u2013 compound 4, GC376, and MAC-5576 \u2013 as inhibitors of the SARS-CoV-2 3CL protease. Structures of each of these compounds in complex with the protease revealed strategies for further development, as well as general principles for designing SARS-CoV-2 3CL protease inhibitors. These compounds may therefore serve as leads for the basis of building effective SARS-CoV-2 3CL protease inhibitors.</jats:p>",
